# SmartCS Project Conventions

## Git Commit Conventions
- All commit messages MUST be in English following Conventional Commits
- Types: feat/fix/refactor/build/chore/docs/test
- Format: `type(scope): description`

## Commit History (recent first)
- feat(agent): add multi-intent detection and is_multi_intent support in router
- feat(agent): add write tools - refund_status_lookup, ticket_update, customer_feedback_submit, loyalty_points_redeem, coupon_apply
- feat(agent): enable AgentCommunicator in workflow for simple tasks and register supervisor
- feat(agent): add asyncio timeout control and error handling with TimeoutError fallback
- feat(agent): add LRU/TTL to WorkingMemory with background cleanup thread
- feat(agent): add file backup for Redis degradation in short_term memory
- feat(agent): enhance vector search with SentenceTransformer embedding
- feat(agent): add token usage statistics with TokenCounter
- feat(agent): add OpenTelemetry support with fallback to InMemoryTracer
- test(agent): update tests for new tools and auth requirements

